value.name: World Telephone Numbering Guide
value.snippet: 10 October 1997 - 6 to 7 digit numbers. An extra digit was added to 6-digit numbers in Senegal on 10 October 1997. There was no permissive dialling period. The new 7-digit format took immediate effect, although callers to old numbers would receive a recorded message giving information about the numbering change.
